Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.97,0:01:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的星星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.64,0:01:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.77,0:01:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tim，总有一天会有人从那片星海中来迎接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.51,0:01:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来迎接我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.64,0:01:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错．这片星空上的某个地方有个很想念你的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.25,0:01:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢，Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.68,0:01:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.66,0:02:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七话 试练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.99,0:02:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是Timothy·Constance先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.53,0:02:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,l3岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出生于Primavera行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其母是Marianne·Constance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.97,0:02:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他的父亲是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.47,0:02:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ablert·Rosenfelt
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.31,0:02:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ablert·Rosenfelt，最近去世的Rosenfelt财团族长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.78,0:02:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenfelt财团？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.98,0:02:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总资产占全银河系金融总额的6.82%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.85,0:02:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最新的统计显示为7.14%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.62,0:02:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～那他是大少爷啰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Timothy·Constance先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Albert先生留下了遗言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.87,0:02:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指定他为下一任继承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过必须在指定的期限内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.00,0:02:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在特定的地方确认是他本人 这件事情才算成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以标准时间来看的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.74,0:02:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有36小时l3分58秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果无法确认的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.42,0:03:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承的资格就会被取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.75,0:03:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～那多可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后有关系的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会为了事业、权力展开争夺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.93,0:03:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该要同时通知指定地点的所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.36,0:03:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为资料受损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致无法辨识正确地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.77,0:03:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经故意对外放出假消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.47,0:03:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但金融管理局似乎在背后进行了一些动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的特别任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在修复的情报中找出原本被指定的行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.21,0:03:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在期限之内将Constance先生平安送达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.08,0:03:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以当成线索的只有这些吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DNA鉴定之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.86,0:03:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在Albert·Rosenfelt所诞生的行星…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.79,0:03:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere 怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.43,0:03:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在用网络搜寻中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.10,0:03:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找个人情报是很不容易的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.27,0:03:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 本来就不可能太简单吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.64,0:04:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且是上流社会的人的话那就更是难上加难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用紧张喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Constance先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.48,0:04:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会好好保住你的遗产继承权的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.75,0:04:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要叫我“先生”好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像不是我的名字似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.72,0:04:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boldor星系…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Farandole行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在银河系的另一端呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要经过空间跳跃一瞬间就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.25,0:04:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫困的男孩子在魔法棒下摇身变成大富翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～好浪漫哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像是最近看过的故事书一样耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我们也走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跟丢的话 可是会被念个半死的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私奔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸为了跟妈妈结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃了继承权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.71,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经一度脱离了Ronsenfelt财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.48,0:05:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在Primavera行星从事农业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.78,0:05:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸用的是本名Cillford
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.12,0:05:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最后父亲还是留下了我跟妈妈回家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.56,0:05:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承袭Albert之名成为家族之主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.63,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连父亲的容貌也不记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道自己跟Ronsenfelt家族有关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从妈妈去世以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.17,0:05:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直在爷爷的农场工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.77,0:05:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 最近GOTT来了消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.25,0:05:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才第一次听爷爷谈起这件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.42,0:05:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 也真是个任性的父亲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.25,0:05:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都放着你们母子不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等有了万一 又希望你能够继承他的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.79,0:05:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够啰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.76,0:06:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 还让你在GOTT或金融管理局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些大人们之间被叫来唤去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.56,0:06:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像搞错地点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会？搜寻的结果确实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.90,0:06:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的是你父亲的出生地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.13,0:06:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只知道爸爸的名字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.34,0:06:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.97,0:06:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸改用Albert这个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跟我和妈妈分开之后的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.08,0:06:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.21,0:06:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Albert并不是我爸爸 而是陌生人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.48,0:06:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.45,0:07:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sylvia星系的…Silvana行星？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Tim的父亲成为第25代族长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.92,0:07:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承Albert之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.33,0:07:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并被认定为财团继承人的星球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩两个标准小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉勉强强呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.97,0:07:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石群接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时形成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.31,0:07:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的偶然呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 警告意味很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.11,0:07:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是绕远路的话就会来不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.02,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.92,0:07:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.39,0:07:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.49,0:07:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.59,0:07:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 男孩子就得这样才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.50,0:07:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？刚刚那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.38,0:08:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Viola！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cesario
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小Lumi、小Ec
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别这样叫我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小Ec 就是小Ec呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.16,0:08:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 随便你啦 他们是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Viola跟Cesario
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.63,0:08:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她们俩人的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们俩个怎么会来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是局长拜托我们偷偷保护你们的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石交给我们的Fenice扫除掉就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快点去Silvana
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.74,0:08:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的多谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.91,0:08:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系、没关系 不过你们之后得请客喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.38,0:08:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？又得请？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.65,0:08:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？中国菜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意大利菜比较好啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不也是吃中国菜吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就决定吃意大利菜好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.43,0:08:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待、好期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还是老样子一点都没变耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.60,0:08:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们永远都相亲相爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小Lumi跟小Ec也很要好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比不上我跟Cesario
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.04,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是挺不错 只是很会精打细算罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.37,0:09:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢…我觉得GOTT的人应该是更…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我们是那种让人不能不绷紧神经的人 是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.45,0:09:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种人都有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是GOTT或是这世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.69,0:09:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了如果无法决定继承人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.60,0:09:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将由我们委员会全权负责今后的运营
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.47,0:09:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在猎户座腕部区的经营收支这期也有盈余呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.47,0:09:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个区域的负责人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代代都是由我们家的人所担任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.88,0:09:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经由这次的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.01,0:09:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能在财务掌管这方面获得更多的权责吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.08,0:09:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵～锵～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.92,0:09:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.05,0:09:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenfelt财团的继承人到达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.83,0:10:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个隔间是干嘛用的呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫生防护罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫生防护罩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监定完毕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Timothy·Constance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过确认 证实与
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Albert·Rosenfelt以及Marianne Constance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人的DNA排序一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 事情应该会更没完没了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看来是赶上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来似乎正在举行宴会的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.69,0:10:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对一定会再发生一些事情吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.79,0:11:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就等着瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么衣服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.05,0:11:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就吃不到料理了呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.51,0:11:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“贵族阶级”是以完全未接受过\N“身体适应处理”为傲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.02,0:11:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯粹血统主义者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.05,0:11:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rosenfelt家族也是其中之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.69,0:11:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这些人对他们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过算是杂菌而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Timothy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.13,0:11:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后将在这些人之中生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.37,0:11:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛马？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.80,0:11:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然骑马是妇女们的嗜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.51,0:11:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但以机械马竞速 可是我们一族的传统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.68,0:11:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是族里的男性 没有人不会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.21,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械马是一项能测试出勇气与智慧的竞赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.02,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必让我们拜见一下新统帅者的技巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.42,0:12:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可、可是我对机械马…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那真是失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.59,0:12:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了你并没有受过贵族阶级的教育
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.67,0:12:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然身为我族的一员却在边境的开发中行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.50,0:12:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被庶民的女孩给骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但遗传基因是骗不了人的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.81,0:12:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我赢了赛马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.98,0:12:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就愿意承认我是继承人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.75,0:12:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 要是赢不了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.55,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能够自行承认自己并没有继承的资格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.92,0:12:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.05,0:12:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想後悔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快为族长备马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.66,0:12:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那个必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.13,0:12:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Donnersclac借你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.10,0:12:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给这些家伙们一点颜色瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.40,0:12:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是 为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要理由吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.91,0:12:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说的一样吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.28,0:12:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.35,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到参加者变的这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.66,0:13:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他们都有老练的教官在指导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.66,0:13:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.06,0:13:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说也有我在嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像在盘算着什么喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.67,0:13:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可务必要小心提防
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.71,0:13:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.28,0:13:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错喔 再提高一点速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还蛮不赖的嘛 族长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是庶民就要像个庶民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.46,0:13:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是在受伤之前快点回家去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是干这种小心眼的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛总是伴随着危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来这是贵族的嗜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.11,0:14:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庶民是不会懂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗？ 可别被甩下去了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给过分淘气的少爷们一点小小的惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害呀！Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.59,0:14:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 Mr…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.23,0:14:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…嗯，这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友们都叫我Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0K Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.77,0:14:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tim 来了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一台也有参加吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是混在出场者之中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个完全是战斗用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专业级的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你负责操纵Donner
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们让我来负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.39,0:14:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.96,0:14:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金融管理局的ES成员吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.56,0:14:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有陨石的欢迎仪式还不够过瘾吗？同行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为ES成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.10,0:15:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还以真面目示人似乎是你们GOTT的传统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也是一件极度愚蠢的事情！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙面是坏人才会做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.44,0:15:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市场可是这么决定的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.08,0:15:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tim 喷射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.78,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.28,0:15:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Donner 钢丝腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞这种鬼玩意儿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.57,0:15:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错哦 Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是你爸爸遗传给你的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？ Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.99,0:15:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.60,0:16:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Titano！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小Ec
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.77,0:16:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是GOTT的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.64,0:16:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.21,0:16:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Titano的装甲是特制的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.18,0:16:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甩他出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人如果手牵手的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.30,0:16:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以控制分子的结合力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.41,0:16:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果手没有牵上的话就不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦 Cesario、Viola
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.58,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来就等你吃意大利料理啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.42,0:17:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.76,0:17:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cesario 手…手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.56,0:17:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.30,0:17:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中国菜、就吃中国菜好了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.94,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏心眼 哼～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使拥有一个出生于开发中星球的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.58,0:17:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也同样能够具备勇气 这件事你们能接受了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.02,0:17:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲的选择似乎是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.33,0:17:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委任书…就交给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你们能了解就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.01,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你帮了我这么多忙 但…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…从一开始就打算这么做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.91,0:18:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想向他们这群人讨回妈妈的名誉而以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意再重新考虑一下吗？ Timothy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.46,0:18:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.79,0:18:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Isaac·Rosenfelt
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的祖父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖父？ 爷爷吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会…会长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不是在静养中吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 将你的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.74,0:18:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你的母亲身边夺走的 正是我本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会跟你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.45,0:18:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为财团需要Albert的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.48,0:18:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这么说来 爸爸并没有抛弃我们母子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.32,0:18:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道Albert的遗言後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我感到相当怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.99,0:18:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的适合担任本财团的继承人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得必须亲自测试看看才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.90,0:18:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.70,0:18:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 局长早就知道指定的是哪个星球啰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.34,0:19:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是没想到这些家伙居然会如此的胡作非为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.94,0:19:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿一定得好好的惩罚惩罚他们才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.61,0:19:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎已经能够理解爸爸为什么会单独回家族来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.59,0:19:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸比任何人都了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.32,0:19:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在平常环境下成长的人 要在贵族阶级中生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是件多么辛苦的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.80,0:19:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸会离开我们母子这都是出自於爸爸对我们的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.77,0:19:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 依然指定我为继承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.97,0:19:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定也是为了让我能够对自己的人生有选择的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.44,0:19:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是Tim…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.15,0:19:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有权利选择自己的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论星星告诉了你什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.19,0:19:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的道路 还是必须由你自己来决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.06,0:19:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然…我没办法马上做出决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.96,0:20:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果因为没有族长而造成整个家族分崩离析的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如顺理继承比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.30,0:20:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Timothy下定决心之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承人的问题就先保留不谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这段期间内我会先辅助族长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.04,0:20:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后万一Timothy发生了什么意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.28,0:20:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就立刻将Rosenfelt财团分割解体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么办！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.89,0:20:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.92,0:20:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以慢慢考虑的Tim
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.59,0:20:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的人生是属于你自己的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 我觉得你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.03,0:20:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都看到了吧？ Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.71,0:20:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 希望你能好好的说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影像证据？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.12,0:20:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.16,0:21:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金融管理局妨碍我们工作的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.43,0:21:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子 以后我们就能牵制他们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了拍下这个影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.90,0:21:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才让 Armbrust故意怂恿财团的人是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.44,0:21:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们以继承权为赌注展开比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.31,0:21:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我相信 你们一定能够保护得了他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.05,0:21:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你们可以解散回去了
